OL,3,CTram passenger involved in fatal
OL,4,Cstruggle released without charge
OL,6,FA tram passenger arrested after the
OL,7,Fdeath of a man who attacked him with a
OL,8,Fknife will not face criminal charges.
OL,10,FNottinghamshire Police said officers
OL,11,Fhad concluded that the man, who was
OL,12,Farrested on suspicion of murder in
OL,13,FNottingham in June last year, was
OL,14,Facting in self-defence when he was
OL,15,Fattacked with a knife.
OL,17,FIn a statement confirming that the
OL,18,Fman, who is aged in his 20s, has been
OL,19,Freleased without charge, officers said
OL,20,FCCTV footage of the incident had been
OL,21,Ftaken into account.
