OL,3,CTram passenger involved in fatal
OL,4,Cstruggle released without charge
OL,6,FThe force said 32-year-old Kyle
OL,7,FKnowles was pronounced dead at the
OL,8,Fscene, having been injured after
OL,9,Fboarding a tram armed with a knife in
OL,10,FBulwell at 11.04am on Monday June 26.
OL,12,FKnowles approached the passenger, who
OL,13,Fwas not named in the statement, and
OL,14,Fbegan an unprovoked attack, police
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FIt is known that the passenger
OL,18,Fsustained serious stab wounds to his
OL,19,Fhands as he attempted to defend
OL,20,Fhimself, and during the struggle,
OL,21,FKnowles was stabbed.
