OL,6,FThe tram then came to a halt at
OL,7,FHighbury Vale tram stop, where the
OL,8,Fpassenger was arrested.
OL,10,FDue to the passenger's suspected
OL,11,Finvolvement in the incident, the
OL,12,FProbation Service recalled him to
OL,13,Fprison because he was in breach of his
OL,14,Flicence for an offence committed in
OL,15,F2016.
