OL,6,F"Keeping people safe in our city and
OL,7,Fcommunities is our priority and we
OL,8,Fwill continue to do all that we can to
OL,9,Ftarget the minority of people who
OL,10,Fcarry or use knives.
OL,12,F"We have dedicated teams that work
OL,13,Falongside our uniformed officers every
OL,14,Fday to tackle knife crime and we
OL,15,Fproactively work with our partners to
OL,16,Fdeter young people away from this
OL,17,Flifestyle."
